title: International Factball: Italy v Switzerland
content: The QI Elves in association with www.visitengland.com bring you the ninth episode of this No Such Thing As A Fish Factball special - the only football podcast that has absolutely nothing to do with football. Today Andrew Hunter Murray (@andrewhunterm), James Harkin (@jamesharkin), Anne Miller (@miller_anne) and Anna Ptaszynski (@nosuchthing) pit Italy against Switzerland to find out which is the most Quite Interesting country.
